dct_description_sm: This tabular data, prepared by Data You Can Use, presents share of vacant housing in 2018 by census tract in the city of Milwaukee, Wisconsin. The data is sourced from the Milwaukee City Water Department file of properties where whater service has been shut off, and utilizes 2020 Census tracts. For more information, please visit Data You Can Use.
